---
import carey_headshot from '../assets/headshots/carey_headshot.jpg';
import family72 from '../assets/marketing/family72.jpg';
---
  <section id="about" class="py-16 px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-tertiary mb-4">All About YAM</h2>

    <p class="text-base text-gray-700 text-left">
      <img src={family72.src} alt="Family lifestyle photo" class="float-right w-52 h-auto ml-4 mb-2 rounded shadow-md" />
      YAM is a telehealth-first practice serving young adults in Nevada with evidence-based, inclusive care.
    </p>

    <p class="text-base text-gray-700 text-left">
      <img src={carey_headshot.src} alt="Carey Roselee, Pediatric NP" class="float-left w-32 h-auto mr-4 mb-2 rounded shadow-md" />
      I’m Carey, a board-certified Pediatric Nurse Practitioner with over a decade of experience caring for children and teens in emergency medicine. I created this practice to offer a more personal, accessible, and empowering approach to healthcare—right from home.
    </p>

    <p class="text-base text-gray-700 text-left">
      Whether you're a parent with questions or a teen looking for a safe space to talk, my goal is to provide trusted medical care with empathy, clarity, and zero judgment.
    </p>
  </section>
